# Database Schema Rules

When modifying database schemas or Drizzle configuration, YOU MUST READ:

1. **Schema Architecture**: `docs/architecture/03-database-schema.md`
2. **Drizzle Rules**: `.claude/rules/backend/drizzle.md`

## Key Principles

- **Location**: Feature schemas in `packages/drizzle/src/schema/features/{name}/index.ts`
- **Naming Convention**:

| 항목              | 스타일                   | 예시                                    |
| :---------------- | :----------------------- | :-------------------------------------- |
| File              | `kebab-case`             | `index.ts` (feature 디렉토리)            |
| Table Variable    | `camelCase`              | `blogPosts`                             |
| DB Table Name     | `{feature}_{entity}`     | `blog_posts`, `blog_blogs` (메인 테이블) |
| DB Enum Name      | `{feature}_{name}`       | `blog_post_status`, `community_type`    |
| DB Column Name    | `snake_case`             | `created_at`, `is_published`            |
| Column Variable   | `camelCase`              | `createdAt`, `isPublished`              |
| Index Name        | `idx_{table}_{column}`   | `idx_blog_posts_author`                 |

### Feature Prefix 규칙 (필수)

- Feature 스키마의 **모든** 테이블/enum은 `{feature}_` prefix 필수
- 메인 테이블도 예외 없음: `board_boards` (O), `boards` (X)
- Core 스키마(`profiles`, `files`, `roles` 등)는 prefix 없음

## Example

```typescript
// packages/drizzle/src/schema/features/blog/index.ts
export const blogStatusEnum = pgEnum("blog_post_status", ["draft", "published"]);

export const blogs = pgTable("blog_blogs", {         // 메인 테이블도 prefix 필수
  ...baseColumns(),
  name: varchar("name", { length: 100 }).notNull(),
});

export const blogPosts = pgTable("blog_posts", {
  ...baseColumns(),
  title: varchar("title", { length: 200 }).notNull(),
  isPublished: boolean("is_published").default(false),  // DB: snake_case
  createdAt: timestamp("created_at").defaultNow(),      // DB: snake_case
});
```
